project: 3D Solar System Simulation
description: >
A 3D solar system simulation built using Three.js and vanilla JavaScript.
Features include orbiting planets, individual speed controls, background stars,
and interactive camera.

requirements:

- Modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge)
- Optional: Live Server for smooth local testing

run_steps:

- Step 1: Download or clone the project folder
- Step 2: Open the folder in a code editor (e.g., VS Code)
- Step 3: Open 'index.html' directly in a web browser
- OR
- Step 3 (recommended): Use Live Server to run 'index.html' locally
  instructions:
  - Install Live Server extension in VS Code
  - Right-click
